casebody.data:
Oscar MINAYA, Petitioner,
v.
UNITED STATES. No. 19-5308 Supreme Court of the United States. November 4, 2019

On petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit. Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis and petition for writ of certiorari granted. Judgment vacated, and case remanded to the United States Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit for further consideration in *464light of United States v. Davis, 588 U.S. ---, 139 S.Ct. 2319, 204 L.Ed.2d 757 (2019).
